- Reorder by confidence (validated ECPs first)

**Update ./brand/learnings.md:**
```
## What Works
- [2026-02-20] [/ecp-validation] Landing page smoke test validated "Fintech B2C" ECP (137 signups, 8.2% conversion)
- [2026-02-20] [/ecp-validation] Interviews confirmed €10/month price point (18/18 said "yes" to €10, 12/18 said "no" to €15)
```

